doc.after: In the British Armed Forces NCOs are divided into two categories Lance corporals including lance bombardiers and corporals including lance sergeants bombardiers and lance corporals of horse are junior NCOs Sergeants including corporals of horse staff sergeants including colour sergeants and staff corporals and RAF chief technicians and flight sergeants are senior NCOs
